channel.title: FTP.exe
channel.description:
Ok hi. So I am working on this one project for my dad. It uses FTP.exe that comes with windows. So I finished it, it works fine on my computer, but it keeps screwing up on my dads'. After a bit of testing, I found out that the ftp utility doesn't work and always gets timeouted. I can open, login, but I can't upload anything; I always get timeout. His firewall is completely off, any antivirus has been shut down.
It works fine on my computer. Any suggestions?
